-- India’s ONGC Offers 700,000 Barrels of Sokol Crude for May
-- B y   R a m s e y   A l - R i k a b i
-- 2012-03-22T13:10:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-22/india-s-ongc-offers-700-000-barrels-of-sokol-crude-for-may-1-.html
ONGC Videsh Ltd., the overseas unit
of  India ’s  Oil & Natural Gas Corp. (ONGC) , offered to sell 700,000
barrels of Sokol crude for loading May 26 to May 29 from
 Russia ’s Far East, according to a notice sent to potential
buyers. Bids are due March 28.  Details of the offer are as follow:  To contact the reporter on this story:
